<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>حجوزات السفر - رحلات برية، جوية وفنادق</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #BFB3A4;
            --secondary-color: #A60303;
            --accent-color-1: #A66D03;
            --accent-color-2: #038C7F;
            --text-color: #333;
            --light-text: #fff;
            --bg-light: #f9f9f9;
            --shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            color: var(--text-color);
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header Styles */
        header {
            background-color: var(--light-text);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .header-top {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 5%;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-left: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--light-text);
        }

        .header-controls {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .language-currency {
            display: flex;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

            .language-currency select {
                border: none;
                background: transparent;
                margin-left: 10px;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

        .nav-menu {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
        }

            .nav-menu a {
                text-decoration: none;
                color: var(--text-color);
                margin: 0 15px;
                font-weight: 500;
                transition: var(--transition);
                position: relative;
            }

                .nav-menu a:hover {
                    color: var(--secondary-color);
                }

                .nav-menu a::after {
                    content: '';
                    position: absolute;
                    bottom: -5px;
                    left: 0;
                    width: 0;
                    height: 2px;
                    background-color: var(--secondary-color);
                    transition: var(--transition);
                }

                .nav-menu a:hover::after {
                    width: 100%;
                }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 500px;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523531294919-4bcd7c65e216?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--light-text);
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

            .hero::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                bottom: 0;
                background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--secondary-color) 0%, transparent 50%);
                opacity: 0.3;
                animation: gradientShift 8s ease-in-out infinite;
            }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 0 20px;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            animation: textGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease;
        }

        .hero-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            color: var(--light-text);
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: var(--transition);
            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

            .hero-btn:hover {
                background-color: transparent;
                color: var(--light-text);
                transform: translateY(-3px);
            }

        /* Tabs Section */
        .tabs-section {
            padding: 60px 5%;
            background-color: var(--light-text);
        }

        .tabs-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .tabs-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .tab-btn {
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            position: relative;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

            .tab-btn.active {
                color: var(--secondary-color);
            }

                .tab-btn.active::after {
                    content: '';
                    position: absolute;
                    bottom: -1px;
                    left: 0;
                    width: 100%;
                    height: 3px;
                    background-color: var(--secondary-color);
                    animation: slideIn 0.3s ease;
                }

        .tab-content {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
        }

            .tab-content.active {
                display: block;
            }

        .search-form {
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            animation: slideUp 0.5s ease;
        }

        .form-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 0 -10px;
        }

        .form-group {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
            padding: 0 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

            .form-group label {
                display: block;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
                font-weight: 500;
            }

            .form-group input, .form-group select {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 12px 15px;
                border: 1px solid #ddd;
                border-radius: 5px;
                transition: var(--transition);
            }

                .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus {
                    border-color: var(--primary-color);
                    outline: none;
                    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(191, 179, 164, 0.2);
                    transform: translateY(-2px);
                }

        .search-btn {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            color: var(--light-text);
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 10px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

            .search-btn:hover {
                background-color: var(--accent-color-1);
                transform: translateY(-2px);
            }

            .search-btn::after {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                top: 50%;
                left: 50%;
                width: 5px;
                height: 5px;
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
                opacity: 0;
                border-radius: 100%;
                transform: scale(1, 1) translate(-50%);
                transform-origin: 50% 50%;
            }

            .search-btn:hover::after {
                animation: ripple 1s ease-out;
            }

        /* Offers Section */
        .offers-section {
            padding: 60px 5%;
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

            .section-title::after {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                bottom: 0;
                left: 50%;
                transform: translateX(-50%);
                width: 100px;
                height: 3px;
                background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
                animation: widthGrow 1.5s ease;
            }

        .offers-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .offer-card {
            background-color: var(--light-text);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: var(--transition);
            position: relative;
        }

            .offer-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }

            .offer-card::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                height: 4px;
                background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent-color-2), var(--accent-color-1));
                transform: scaleX(0);
                transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            }

            .offer-card:hover::before {
                transform: scaleX(1);
            }

        .offer-img {
            height: 200px;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .offer-card:hover .offer-img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .offer-content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .offer-title {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        .offer-price {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--accent-color-1);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .offer-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--accent-color-2);
            color: var(--light-text);
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: var(--transition);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

            .offer-btn:hover {
                background-color: var(--primary-color);
                transform: translateX(5px);
            }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #2c2c2c;
            color: var(--light-text);
            padding: 60px 5% 30px;
        }

        .footer-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .footer-column h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

            .footer-column h3::after {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                bottom: 0;
                left: 0;
                width: 50px;
                height: 2px;
                background-color: var(--accent-color-2);
                animation: widthGrow 1s ease;
            }

        .footer-column ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

            .footer-column ul li {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                transition: var(--transition);
            }

                .footer-column ul li:hover {
                    transform: translateX(5px);
                }

                .footer-column ul li a {
                    color: #ccc;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    transition: var(--transition);
                }

                    .footer-column ul li a:hover {
                        color: var(--primary-color);
                    }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

            .social-links a {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                width: 40px;
                height: 40px;
                background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
                border-radius: 50%;
                margin-left: 10px;
                transition: var(--transition);
                text-decoration: none;
                color: white;
            }

                .social-links a:hover {
                    background-color: var(--accent-color-2);
                    transform: translateY(-3px);
                }

        .footer-bottom {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 30px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        /* Animations - Keyframes */
        @@keyframes fadeInUp {
            from

        {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        }

        @@keyframes fadeIn {
            from

        {
            opacity: 0;
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        }

        @@keyframes slideIn {
            from

        {
            width: 0;
        }

        to {
            width: 100%;
        }

        }

        @@keyframes slideUp {
            from

        {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        }

        @@keyframes pulse {
            0%

        {
            transform: scale(1);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(166, 3, 3, 0.7);
        }

        70% {
            transform: scale(1);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(166, 3, 3, 0);
        }

        100% {
            transform: scale(1);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(166, 3, 3, 0);
        }

        }

        @@keyframes textGlow {
            from

        {
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        to {
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3), 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        }

        @@keyframes gradientShift {
            0%

        {
            transform: translateX(-100%);
        }

        50% {
            transform: translateX(100%);
        }

        100% {
            transform: translateX(-100%);
        }

        }

        @@keyframes ripple {
            0%

        {
            transform: scale(0, 0);
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        100% {
            transform: scale(20, 20);
            opacity: 0;
        }

        }

        @@keyframes widthGrow {
            from

        {
            width: 0;
        }

        to {
            width: 100px;
        }

        }

        /* Loading Animation */
        .loading {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);
            border-radius: 50%;
            border-top-color: #fff;
            animation: spin 1s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @@keyframes spin {
            to

        {
            transform: rotate(360deg);
        }

        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @@media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header-top

        {
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .nav-menu {
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

            .nav-menu a {
                margin: 5px 10px;
            }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .tabs-header {
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .tab-btn {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .form-row {
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .form-group {
            min-width: 100%;
        }

        .hero-btn {
            animation: none;
        }

        }</style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <div class="header-top">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon"><i class="fas fa-plane"></i></div>
                سفريات
            </div>
            <div class="header-controls">
                <div class="language-currency">
                    <select id="currency">
                        <option value="SAR">SAR</option>
                        <option value="USD">USD</option>
                        <option value="EUR">EUR</option>
                    </select>
                    <select id="language">
                        <option value="ar">العربية</option>
                        <option value="en">English</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav-menu">
            <a href="#">الرئيسية</a>
            <a href="#">رحلات الطيران</a>
            <a href="#">رحلات الحافلات</a>
            <a href="#">الفنادق</a>
            <a href="#">عروض خاصة</a>
            <a href="#">اتصل بنا</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>استمتع بأفضل عروض السفر</h1>
            <p>احجز رحلاتك بسهولة وأمان مع أفضل العروض على الطيران، الحافلات والفنادق</p>
            <a href="#" class="hero-btn">استكشف العروض</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Tabs Section -->
    <section class="tabs-section">
        <div class="tabs-container">
            <div class="tabs-header">
                <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="land">رحلات برية</button>
                <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="flight">رحلات جوية</button>
                <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="hotels">فنادق</button>
            </div>

            <!-- Land Trips Tab -->
            <div class="tab-content active" id="land-tab">
                <div class="search-form">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="from-land">من</label>
                            <input type="text" id="from-land" placeholder="المدينة أو المحطة">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="to-land">إلى</label>
                            <input type="text" id="to-land" placeholder="المدينة أو المحطة">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="departure-land">تاريخ المغادرة</label>
                            <input type="date" id="departure-land">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="return-land">تاريخ العودة (اختياري)</label>
                            <input type="date" id="return-land">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="search-btn">ابحث عن رحلات</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Flight Trips Tab -->
            <div class="tab-content" id="flight-tab">
                <div class="search-form">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="from-flight">من</label>
                            <input type="text" id="from-flight" placeholder="المدينة أو المطار">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="to-flight">إلى</label>
                            <input type="text" id="to-flight" placeholder="المدينة أو المطار">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="departure-flight">تاريخ المغادرة</label>
                            <input type="date" id="departure-flight">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="return-flight">تاريخ العودة (اختياري)</label>
                            <input type="date" id="return-flight">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="passengers">عدد المسافرين</label>
                            <select id="passengers">
                                <option value="1">1 مسافر</option>
                                <option value="2">2 مسافرين</option>
                                <option value="3">3 مسافرين</option>
                                <option value="4">4 مسافرين</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="class">فئة المقعد</label>
                            <select id="class">
                                <option value="economy">السياحية</option>
                                <option value="business">رجال الأعمال</option>
                                <option value="first">الأولى</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="search-btn">ابحث عن رحلات</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Hotels Tab -->
            <div class="tab-content" id="hotels-tab">
                <div class="search-form">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="destination">الوجهة</label>
                            <input type="text" id="destination" placeholder="المدينة أو الفندق">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="check-in">تاريخ الوصول</label>
                            <input type="date" id="check-in">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="check-out">تاريخ المغادرة</label>
                            <input type="date" id="check-out">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="rooms">الغرف</label>
                            <select id="rooms">
                                <option value="1">1 غرفة</option>
                                <option value="2">2 غرفة</option>
                                <option value="3">3 غرفة</option>
                                <option value="4">4 غرفة</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="adults">البالغين</label>
                            <select id="adults">
                                <option value="1">1 بالغ</option>
                                <option value="2">2 بالغين</option>
                                <option value="3">3 بالغين</option>
                                <option value="4">4 بالغين</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="children">الأطفال</label>
                            <select id="children">
                                <option value="0">0 أطفال</option>
                                <option value="1">1 طفل</option>
                                <option value="2">2 أطفال</option>
                                <option value="3">3 أطفال</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="search-btn">ابحث عن فنادق</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Special Offers Section -->
    <section class="offers-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">عروض خاصة</h2>
        <div class="offers-grid">
            <div class="offer-card">
                <div class="offer-img" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566073771259-6a8506099945?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80');"></div>
                <div class="offer-content">
                    <h3 class="offer-title">رحلة إلى إسطنبول</h3>
                    <p class="offer-desc">استمتع برحلة مميزة إلى إسطنبول مع إقامة في فندق 5 نجوم</p>
                    <div class="offer-price">1,499 ريال</div>
                    <a href="#" class="offer-btn">احجز الآن</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="offer-card">
                <div class="offer-img" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512453979798-5ea266f8880c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80');"></div>
                <div class="offer-content">
                    <h3 class="offer-title">عطلة في دبي</h3>
                    <p class="offer-desc">عروض خاصة على الفنادق والجولات السياحية في دبي</p>
                    <div class="offer-price">899 ريال</div>
                    <a href="#" class="offer-btn">احجز الآن</a>
